{"tid":1230291,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"大家遊行時可唔可以唔好嘻嘻哈哈","createTime":"2019-06-16T07:04:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-16T07:30:41.000Z","uid":179167,"like":27,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"aa516f38b64f5b796cc430c6cc5ac2672d79403c","tid":1230291,"uid":179167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T07:04:57.000Z","msg":"我知成班friend去有時會忍唔住吹下水，笑下<br />\n上星期都經常有咁嘅情況<br />\n但今日，請各位尊重傷者、死者、仲有一眾被捕義士，今日唔係應該笑嘅日子<br />\n希望各位盡量注意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b03a06f4e8fdd230ed40d39b8b1471fd7bb760a","tid":1230291,"uid":261384,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T07:05:49.000Z","msg":"雖然係咁但係大家樂觀一點都可以嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b3a24d987a67b293b04ee450c70dc1e569dadf9","tid":1230291,"uid":179167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4b03a06f4e8fdd230ed40d39b8b1471fd7bb760a","tid":1230291,"uid":261384,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T07:05:49.000Z","msg":"雖然係咁但係大家樂觀一點都可以嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T07:08:23.000Z","msg":"我明，雖然大家好憎階段性勝利<br />\n但呢幾日我地始終取得左幾好嘅進展，好多香港人都會鬆左一口氣<br />\n但千祈唔好忘記呢啲進展係用血同命換返嚟"},{"pid":"c19204e180522a7825423fd7b795c9106d2e7b17","tid":1230291,"uid":229955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T07:08:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Y9hCJKF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FY9hCJKF.jpg&h=0756c303&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">大會宣布 提前出發 @ 14:30 <br />\n<br />\n1) 由維園 去 金鐘添美道<br />\n2) 2 條 BANNER : 「痛心疾首」 「撤回惡法」 由宗教界 同 一班媽媽帶領<br />\n3) 「痛心疾首」 BANNER 會放喺適當地方 , 畀各市民獻花<br />\n4) 有宗教界負責安排 祈禱會<br />\n5) 有支援抗爭者基金籌款箱<br />\n<br />\n616 黑色大遊行 五大宗旨:<br />\n<br />\n1) 撒回惡法<span style=\"font-size: large;\"></span><br />\n2) 釋放被捕既抗爭者<br />\n3) 我們不是暴徒<br />\n4) 追究黑警開槍責任<br />\n5) 淋病下台</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">黑警冷血，林鄭殺港<br />\n無線新聞，出賣港人</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">香港人加油</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c2752dd772353d540c49fe44526ed0614c18d1c","tid":1230291,"uid":245274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T07:12:21.000Z","msg":"去獵女？獵仔？ 獵荷包，痴漢。<br />\n一樣米都可以養百樣人， 何況係一百萬人。"},{"pid":"3755ff175289479c76638072f554f006c9dbf6c9","tid":1230291,"uid":179167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3c2752dd772353d540c49fe44526ed0614c18d1c","tid":1230291,"uid":245274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T07:12:21.000Z","msg":"去獵女？獵仔？ 獵荷包，痴漢。<br />\n一樣米都可以養百樣人， 何況係一百萬人。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T07:23:00.000Z","msg":"唯有勸得就勸"},{"pid":"9d10ca313e59e691842646c7db445b171578ba34","tid":1230291,"uid":245274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3755ff175289479c76638072f554f006c9dbf6c9","tid":1230291,"uid":179167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3c2752dd772353d540c49fe44526ed0614c18d1c","tid":1230291,"uid":245274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T07:12:21.000Z","msg":"去獵女？獵仔？ 獵荷包，痴漢。<br />\n一樣米都可以養百樣人， 何況係一百萬人。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T07:23:00.000Z","msg":"唯有勸得就勸"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T07:26:42.000Z","msg":"仲有d係會出手打勸佢既人，仲有d係唔會插手既人"},{"pid":"0177220c9a7bd0e33899ea5f4727139de0dbeedd","tid":1230291,"uid":261633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T07:30:17.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8daed04a3c6fb74747e508f0598d3304b4f8756d","tid":1230291,"uid":165840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T07:30:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}